div.div:
1. Decide on a 10 or 14-point game.
2. Decide on a galaxy layout.
3. Randomly determine player seating.
4. Randomly determine the first Speaker.
5. Choose factions.
6. Create the galaxy.
7.Gain starting units, technologies,
tokens, and other cards.
8.Randomly distribute 2 secret objectives
to each player, and each player chooses
1 to keep.
9. Reveal 2 stage I public objectives.
